  "knowledge_nodes": [
    {
      "content": "真空是完全没有阻力的介质（介质密度为零）。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_ab78404c32608954",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "setting.vacuum",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面沟槽经抛光处理，衬以羊皮纸，使用坚硬光滑的青铜球——摩擦和空气阻力可忽略。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_80477297a554f879",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "setting.plane",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "日常生活中，石头比羽毛下落更快，铁球比木球更快。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_93752d842dd5e1d9",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.daily",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落，介质越稠密速度差异越明显；越稀薄差异越不明显。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_45d13455b1e41ca3",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.media",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中，金球、铅球、铜球等重材料球从100腕尺落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_0b9e14832a912361",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.air",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验：不同重量的球沿抛光沟槽滚下，所经距离之比等于时间之比的平方，与球重量无关。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_5e564c2d5cad350c",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.theta",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "物体下落速度与其重量成正比：重物比轻物下落更快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_d0099d7032e8da7f",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.A",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，将重球H与轻球L绑在一起，L拖拽H，复合体HL速度应慢于H单独下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_d342625139e06e59",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.T1",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，复合体HL总重量大于H，因此HL速度应快于H单独下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_e32921ed6aa47710",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.T2",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "T1与T2互相矛盾：复合体HL不能同时慢于H又快于H。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "hyp.T1",
          "hyp.T2"
        ]
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_1f0e716922088e0a",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "rel.T1_contra_T2",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在真空中也应重者更快（A的推论应用于真空条件）。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_ca58d6d2768560c6",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.A_vac",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "介质实验与空气实验的证据表明，在真空中不同重量的物体以相同速率下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_1450596204e16360",
      "source_refs": [
